ldapConnect()

Description
    bool ldapConnect(string $ldapServer)
    Wrapper function for ldap_connect().

Parameters
    ldapServer
    A string containing the hostname of the LDAP server.

Return Values
    Returns a positive LDAP link identifier on success, or FALSE on error.

Examples
    <?php
	...
	$ldapconn = ldapConnect($ldapServer);

	if(!securityUserCheck($username, $password, "ldap", $ldapconn, $ldapDomain)) {
	    ldapDisconnect($ldapconn);
	    return(FALSE);
	}
	...
    ?>

See Also
    ldapLogin()